286. 




                     HENRY HUGHES (24), 


                        PLEADED GUILTY



                     to feloniously forging and uttering a transfer of 300l. new three per cent, stock in the Bank of England; 



                     also, to personating 



                        Robert Gibson, the holder of the said stock'; 



                     also, to forging and uttering a transfer of 200l. stock of the said 



                        Robert Gibson; 



                     also, to personating the holder of the same; 



                     also, to forging a power of attorney to transfer 120l. Consols, the property of 



                        Samuel Dixon; 



                     also, to forging the signatures of the witnesses to the said transfer.
